data.description: This home is LOADED with premium upgrades that you simply won't find with new construction.  Walk into freshly installed, high-grade carpet throughout.  The upper level boasts a large living room with 2 Solatube Skylights and an open concept dining room and kitchen.  High-end Pella slider opens to a 12x16 composite deck.  Kitchen has been completely upgraded since 2013 - quartz countertops, sink/faucet, stone backsplash, and appliances. The primary bedroom has private access to the full bath.  The lower level includes the second living area w/bonus closet, 2 bedrooms with large closets, and utility/laundry room.  High efficiency heat pump water heater. Washer/dryer/water softener included! Spacious garage includes attic stairs for bonus storage. Exterior upgrades include 2023 roof, gutters and drain tiles for gutter/sump pump, black chain link fenced in backyard with gates on each side, 10x12 storage shed and a 3rd lane to the driveway. The lawn was professionally landscape and has been treated each season. Windows have been treated with film for efficiency and daytime privacy. The home is also wired for a generator. Move right in and don't worry about a thing for years!
